{"tid":1080152,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排成日都諗返起個ex","createTime":"2019-03-27T11:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T14:35:26.000Z","uid":161575,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd89d3cf408ab3b8c1938b84d259d95a75610bf0","tid":1080152,"uid":161575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"同個ex一齊咗五年，分咗手已經兩年<br />\n宜家亦都有個新女朋友<br />\n原本以為已經放低咗<br />\n直至幾個月前返工嘅時候撞返佢<br />\n雖然望住佢個人成個感覺變咗好多，好似已經唔係我以前認識嘅佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但由嗰一日開始我就經常諗返起佢<br />\n成日係到諗如果我同佢冇分手宜家會點<br />\n但我又唔係唔愛宜家個女朋友<br />\n每次一諗起個ex嘅時候就會好想忘記哂所有關於佢嘅野<br />\n但當佢係我腦裡面嘅印象愈黎愈模糊嘅時候，我又偏偏好想諗返起同佢相處嘅每一個細節，唔想呢個人就咁係我生命入面消失<br />\n我知道好矛盾，亦都知道未必有咩實質嘅解決辦法幫到我<br />\n所以只係求巴打們開解一下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者如果有巴打有類似嘅情況可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493fe64ddd3c7e7b49842386653ecf25265c8ef3","tid":1080152,"uid":8158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"最愛既係佢？"},{"pid":"8b8703babd61b67acd5f2a09a9795e8800eda9d3","tid":1080152,"uid":161575,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"493fe64ddd3c7e7b49842386653ecf25265c8ef3","tid":1080152,"uid":8158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"最愛既係佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:50:56.000Z","msg":"初戀黎，一定係最愛"},{"pid":"4ec2943116c44a322715c13c006498f56cea5e67","tid":1080152,"uid":180847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"出事喎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1006c61a162b743f5dcd092de5337ea15e056daa","tid":1080152,"uid":161575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ec2943116c44a322715c13c006498f56cea5e67","tid":1080152,"uid":180847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"出事喎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"我都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我真係冇野做到"},{"pid":"c16a426ef893406078f38ab98727e52b4f380c37","tid":1080152,"uid":63003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"冇follow ig fb咩"},{"pid":"7484c1aedd043565c9b9a8e5197577b0291b5301","tid":1080152,"uid":161575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16a426ef893406078f38ab98727e52b4f380c37","tid":1080152,"uid":63003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"冇follow ig fb咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"有 但佢唔係成日post相嗰啲<br />\n一post就係佢而家條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到個心會赤赤痛"},{"pid":"038a3f2a5a26cc286e6e193eec1be24ca3930633","tid":1080152,"uid":166452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:59:27.000Z","msg":"男人最愛一定係初戀？"},{"pid":"40ee62fbf4340f9e2ca9daabcfb4faa17753b7b6","tid":1080152,"uid":243355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ab1a5e6c8d2c8a9258169f6e3428f1b51f7456f","tid":1080152,"uid":8158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b8703babd61b67acd5f2a09a9795e8800eda9d3","tid":1080152,"uid":161575,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"493fe64ddd3c7e7b49842386653ecf25265c8ef3","tid":1080152,"uid":8158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"最愛既係佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:50:56.000Z","msg":"初戀黎，一定係最愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:02:10.000Z","msg":"專心同現任一齊啦 唔好搞咁多嘢 最後咩都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadc9b3b6e041b7c6b03778ec4242719a8f47a90","tid":1080152,"uid":116242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"我呢排都特別掛住ex...<br />\n<br />\n初戀，一齊咗12年，分咗手7年